b'Azuki-chan the Movie': b"It's Valentines' Day, the girls are thinking about the chocolate to give to their love.  Youko is having a party on the Valentines' Day.  The girls refused her invite, but found out that their love are going to her party, even Azuki-chan's brother is going!\n\nYunosuke-kun gave Azuki-chan a chance to give chocolate to him before Youko's party.  Will she be successful in making a chocolate?  Will Yunosuke-kun receive her love?"
